alerts.headline: Wind Advisory issued March 15 at 5:10AM HST until March 16 at 8:00AM HST by NWS Honolulu HI
alerts.description:
* WHAT...Southwest winds 30 to 45 mph with higher gusts.

* WHERE...Big Island Summits.

* WHEN...Until 8 AM HST Sunday.

* IMPACTS...Winds this strong can make driving and walking
dangerous. The winds can forcefully open doors and damage hinges
or slam doors shut, possibly causing injuries.
